<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="tagline">Nigeria's Career Infrastructure Platform</p>
    <h1>About BridgeDegree</h1>
    <p>We build the verified professional identity of Nigerian students — from their first day in university to their first day in a global career. Not a course. Not a bootcamp. Infrastructure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why we exist</h2>
    <p>Nigeria produces over 600,000 graduates every year. Most are qualified. Nearly all are invisible to employers — not because they lack ability, but because the university system produces academic records and nothing else. No verified work history. No published research. No globally legible career profile.</p>
    <p>BridgeDegree was founded in 2026 to solve this at the structural level. We give students a way to build proof while they study — so that by graduation, they hold credentials any employer, anywhere, can verify in seconds.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>We run three programme engines alongside a student's university education:</p>
    <div class="about-values">
      <div class="about-value">
        <div class="icon"><i data-lucide="briefcase"></i></div>
        <h3>Work Experience Engine</h3>
        <p>Structured internships from 200 Level with vetted partners. Performance-tracked, mentor-validated, blockchain-credentialed. So you graduate with 2+ years of documented experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value">
        <div class="icon"><i data-lucide="book-open"></i></div>
        <h3>Publication Pipeline</h3>
        <p>Your final-year project becomes co-authored, submitted to an indexed journal, and part of your permanent academic portfolio — the credential that separates you globally.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value">
        <div class="icon"><i data-lucide="globe"></i></div>
        <h3>Global Mobility Framework</h3>
        <p>Scholarship strategy, SOP development, international CV, ATS calibration, and post-graduation migration support. The tier that turns your proof into global opportunity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top: 32px;">Everything a student produces — every internship, publication, and mentor validation — is aggregated into their <strong>Career Passport</strong>: a single blockchain-credentialed record verifiable by any employer, anywhere, instantly.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Our approach</h2>
    <p>BridgeDegree operates independently of any university. We don't require institutional approval or affiliation. Individual lecturers and departments recommend us to their students — but the platform is not a university product. We work with students at every stage: from 100 Level through NYSC and into postgraduate and global careers.</p>
    <p>We publish our outcomes — student case studies, employer endorsements, and placement data — because trust must be proved, not claimed.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section alt about-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Ready to start?</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Join BridgeDegree and graduate with proof.</p>
    <a href="/students/apply#apply" class="btn-primary">Start My Application <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></a>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact us</a>
  </div>
</section>
